translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やっ、ああっ……！」

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: セルの背中をぬるぬると滑ると、

かなり流されやすいみたいだし、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: she seems pretty easy to go along with things,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスも同じことすればいいよ」

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺がセルさんをマッサージ？」

徐々に自分の手でとろとろにしていくの。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Slowly make her melt with your own hands.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とっても楽しいよ」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The trick is to gradually and steadily approach without rushing~.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So I'm here to give you a massage!"

昨日は随分と気持ち良くして
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She said you felt really good yesterday,

あの、ええっ……！？」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm? Why is your face turning red?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マッサージに普通も何もあるか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is there such a thing as a normal or not normal massage?"

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: oh I see, I guess my massage

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well then... I guess I'll ask you..."
